<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> say something in confidence • say something with confidence</xh5><p> <i>say something in confidence—</i>tell smth. on the understanding that the information is not to be disclosed: McSorley should not even have written down what was <u>said in confidence</u> by Kennedy.</p><p> <i>say something with confidence—</i>say smth. assuredly and with conviction: No one can <u>say with confidence</u> now what the outcome will be.</p> </entry>
